<h2>Instructions on how to play the game</h2>
<p>In rock-paper-scissors, two players will each randomly choose one of three hand signs: rock, paper, or scissors. Both players show their signs at the same time to see who will win.</p>
<p>Rock wins over scissors, Scissors wins over paper and Paper wins over rock.</p>
